  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486110/extras/6519cd35d25f958941dd1f4fbbf0101f.avif?t=1742479867\" width=616 height=120 /></span>Just Cat Slap is a game about two cats fighting for the love of a female cat. However, only one can win her affection! To prove who is truly worthy, they must face off in a slap duel. Quick reflexes will determine who truly deserves her love!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486110/extras/e0eaa06be7d55ef8e3110d354ef9907a.avif?t=1742479867\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486110/extras_big/e0eaa06be7d55ef8e3110d354ef9907a.avif?t=1742479867 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gameplay is simple but challenging. You can only slap your opponent when the exclamation appears, so fast reflexes are key. The game features three difficulty levels and multiple endings depending on whether you win or lose. You can also enjoy local multiplayer with a friend using the same device.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486110/extras/9a833d172e68c08adb35a6385e679fbf.avif?t=1742479867\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486110/extras_big/9a833d172e68c08adb35a6385e679fbf.avif?t=1742479867 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want to challenge a friend? Play local multiplayer on a single device and see who has the fastest reflexes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is my first game, developed entirely as a solo developer. I hope you have fun playing it!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486110/extras/6519cd35d25f958941dd1f4fbbf0101f.avif?t=1742479867\" width=616 height=120 /></span>Just Cat Slap is a game about two cats fighting for the love of a female cat. However, only one can win her affection! To prove who is truly worthy, they must face off in a slap duel. Quick reflexes will determine who truly deserves her love!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486110/extras/e0eaa06be7d55ef8e3110d354ef9907a.avif?t=1742479867\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486110/extras_big/e0eaa06be7d55ef8e3110d354ef9907a.avif?t=1742479867 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gameplay is simple but challenging. You can only slap your opponent when the exclamation appears, so fast reflexes are key. The game features three difficulty levels and multiple endings depending on whether you win or lose. You can also enjoy local multiplayer with a friend using the same device.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486110/extras/9a833d172e68c08adb35a6385e679fbf.avif?t=1742479867\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486110/extras_big/9a833d172e68c08adb35a6385e679fbf.avif?t=1742479867 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want to challenge a friend? Play local multiplayer on a single device and see who has the fastest reflexes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is my first game, developed entirely as a solo developer. I hope you have fun playing it!</p>",
